Description
The table contains information about trailers, including their identification, specifications, and current status. Use cases include tracking trailer acquisition, assessing operational status, and analyzing trailer characteristics such as type and length. This data can help in inventory management and logistical planning.

COLUMN                      |              TYPE                 |     COMMENTS
TRAILER_ID                  |              STRING               |
TRAILER_NUMBER              |              BIGINT               |
TRAILER_TYPE                |              STRING               |
LENGTH FEET                 |              BIGINT               |
MODEL YEAR                  |              BIGINT               |
VIN                         |              STRING               |
ACQUISITON_DATE             |               DATE                |
STATUS                      |              STRING               |
CURRENT_LOCATION            |              STRING               |


--SAMPLE DATA 
Oldest trailer by acquisition date?
---SQL:
        SELECT *
FROM `datawerhouse1`.`bronze`.`trailers`
ORDER BY `acquisition_date` ASC
LIMIT 1;

